  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nAny `truffle` command breaks with\r\n```\r\nTypeError: path must be a string\r\n    at TypeError (native)\r\n    at Object.fs.stat (fs.js:830:11)\r\n    at Object.files (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/node-dir/lib/paths.js:164:8)\r\n```\r\nIssue source is the _minor_ upgrade ()0.1.16->0.1.17) of `node-dir` package which is causing a wider disruption than just `truffle`\r\nhttps://github.com/fshost/node-dir/issues/50\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nrun `truffle compile`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nCommand completes\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\nTruffle commands fail with\r\nTypeError: path must be a string\r\n    at TypeError (native)\r\n    at Object.fs.stat (fs.js:830:11)\r\n    at Object.files (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/node-dir/lib/paths.js:164:8)\r\n    at Object.module.exports.contractFiles (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/ether-pudding/index.js:270:9)\r\n    at Object.module.exports.requireAll (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/ether-pudding/index.js:253:10)\r\n    at Object.Contracts.provision (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/contracts.js:39:13)\r\n    at TruffleInterpreter.provision (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/repl.js:56:13)\r\n    at TruffleInterpreter.start (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/repl.js:24:8)\r\n    at Object.Repl.run (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/repl.js:130:17)\r\n    at /opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/tasks.js:229:19\r\n    at Tasks.(anonymous function) (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/tasks.js:21:5)\r\n    at Command.run (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/command.js:50:5)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/opt/circleci/nodejs/v4.8.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/cli.js:11:9)\r\n    at Module._compile (module.js:409:26)\r\n    at Object.Module._extensions..js (module.js:416:10)\r\n    at Module.load (module.js:343:32\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\nTested with multiple environments and versions.\r\n* Operating System: OSX, Ubuntu\r\n* Truffle version: 2.1.2, 3.2.4\r\n* Ethereum client: parity v1.5.12\r\n* node version: 4.8.3, 4.6.1\r\n* npm version: 3.10.8\r\n",
